title: Nyannya!
description:
The selfish, conniving and ridiculously adorable kitten-prince of a kingdom of cats falls for the royal gardener and is determined to have him whatever the cost. He just needs to get rid of the gardener's lover first!

Chapter 1: Go Prince Sukomaru!
Chapter 2: Prince Sukomaru Writes A Love Letter
Chapter 3: Prince Sukomaru In Summer Festival Clothes
Chapter 4: Prince Sukomaru Meets Taigao
Chapter 5: Longing Mechanism
Chapter 6: Snow-Strewn Hamlet
